### HTTP Status Codes

**ALWAYS** use appropriate HTTP status codes:

```typescript
// 200 - Success
res.json(data);

// 201 - Created
res.status(201).json(newResource);

// 204 - No Content (for DELETE)
res.status(204).send();

// 400 - Bad Request
